Class MapleParserBaseListener

java.lang.Object
net.rotgruengelb.maple.internal.generated.MapleParserBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
MapleParserListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class MapleParserBaseListener extends Object implements MapleParserListener
This class provides an empty implementation of MapleParserListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
